  <brief_title>Injection Management With Betaferon: Influence on Adherence, Patients Satisfaction and Health Related Outcomes (BETAPATH)</brief_title>
  <official_title>BetaferonÂ® Injection Management: Non-interventional Study on Personal Digital Assistant (PDA)Supported Effects on Adherence to a Long-term Injection Therapy (BETAPATH)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
