  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Aim of the BETAPATH study is to evaluate whether the use of a personal digital assistant
      (PDA) can improve the adherence of Multiple Sclerosis patients to a therapy with Betaseron.
      The Personal digital assistant PDA functions as an electronic diary and as an injection
      reminder.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
